98	## 6. Layout Rules
99	
100	### Scaffold Structure
101	
102	- `Scaffold` with `ListView` body
103	- `AppBar`: Title "Cycle Tracking", back button (white/lavender arrow), no trailing icons
104	- `BottomNavigationBar`: Hidden (as per UX spec)
105	- `FAB`: `+` icon to add new cycle entry, positioned bottom-right with safe area respect
106	
107	### AppBar Behavior
108	
109	- Background: `lavenderBloom` (#7C3AED)
110	- Title: "Cycle Tracking" (SemiBold 20sp, white)
111	- Leading: Back button with 48dp touch target
112	- Scroll behavior: Static AppBar (no SliverAppBar needed for simple ListView)
113	
114	### Body Layout
115	
116	- `ListView` with `padding: EdgeInsets.symmetric(horizontal: 16dp, vertical: 24dp)`
117	- Two major sections stacked vertically with 24dp spacing
118	- Bottom padding: 100dp to clear FAB and safe area
119	
120	### FAB Specifications
121	
122	- Size: 56dp diameter
123	- Background: `lavenderBloom` (#7C3AED)
124	- Icon: White, 24dp `Icons.add`
125	- Shadow: Medium diffused shadow (12dp blur)
126	- Press feedback: 200ms scale to 90%
127	- Position: Bottom-right, 16dp from edges, respects safe area bottom
128	
129	---
130	
131	## 7. Sections
132	
133	### Section 1: Current Cycle Card
134	
135	**Description:** Prominent card displaying days since last period, current cycle day, and ovulation window prediction.
136	
137	**Widget Type:** `Card` with `Column` layout inside `SliverToBoxAdapter`
138	
139	**Layout:** Full-width card with 16dp internal padding.
140	
141	**Components:**
142	- Card background: `morningMist` (#FAFAFA), 16dp corner radius, soft shadow
143	- Cycle day badge: Pill-shaped chip with `lavenderBloom` background, white text "Day X"
144	- Days since period: Large number (`displayLarge`) with "days since last period" label
145	- Next period estimate: Row with calendar icon + date prediction
146	- Ovulation window: Row with `blushRose` background pill, egg/flower icon + "Fertile window: [date range]"
147	- Length indicator: Horizontal bar showing cycle progress (filled portion in lavender)
148	
149	**Data Requirements:**
150	- `lastPeriodDate` from `CycleEntryProvider`
151	- `cycleLength` average from `CycleEntryProvider` history
152	- Ovulation calculation: `lastPeriodDate + cycleLength - 14` (assumed ovulation day)
153	- Fertile window: `ovulationDay - 3` to `ovulationDay + 1`
154	
155	**Interactive Elements:**
156	- Tap ovulation window → detail bottom sheet explaining fertile window calculation
157	
158	---
159	
160	### Section 2: Cycle History List
161	
162	**Description:** Chronological list of all logged cycles with visual length indicators.
163	
164	**Widget Type:** `SliverList` with `delegate: SliverChildBuilderDelegate`
165	
166	**Layout:** Vertical list with 12dp gap between items.
167	
168	**Components:**
169	- Section header: "Cycle History" (`headlineMedium`, 24sp)
170	- Each history item Card:
171	  - Start date (formatted: "Jan 15 - Feb 12, 2024") with `titleMedium` style
172	  - Cycle length badge: "28 days" pill with `lavenderTint` background
173	  - Visual bar: Horizontal bar showing relative cycle length (normalized to average)
174	  - Notes preview: First line of notes in `bodyMedium` stoneGrey if present
175	  - Irregular indicator: Small `blushRose` dot if `isIrregular = true`
176	- Empty state: Centered illustration with "No cycles logged yet" message, "Tap + to add your first cycle" subtitle
177	- Add history button at bottom (text button, not part of FAB flow)
178	
179	**Data Requirements:**
180	- All `CycleEntry` records from `CycleEntryProvider`
181	- Sorted by `startDate` descending (most recent first)
182	- `startDate`, `endDate`, `cycleLength`, `notes`, `isIrregular` fields
183	
184	**Interactive Elements:**
185	- Long-press entry → edit/delete bottom sheet
186	- Tap entry → detail bottom sheet with full notes view
187	
188	---
189	
190	### Section 3 (Overlay): New Cycle Entry Bottom Sheet
191	
192	**Description:** Form for logging a new cycle start date and optional notes.
193	
194	**Trigger:** Tap FAB `+`
195	
196	**Widget Type:** `showModalBottomSheet` with `SingleChildScrollView`
197	
198	**Layout:** Bottom sheet with 28dp top corner radius, handle bar, max 90% screen height.
199	
200	**Components:**
201	- Handle bar: 40dp wide, 4dp tall, centered, Stone 300 color
202	- Title: "Log Cycle" (`titleLarge`)
203	- Date picker field: "Period Started" label with date display, tap → `showDatePicker`
204	- Length field (optional): "Cycle Length (days)" numeric input, pre-filled with average
205	- Notes field: Multi-line `TextField` with 56dp min height, hint "Add notes..."
206	- Irregular toggle: `Switch` with label "Irregular cycle"
207	- Action buttons: "Cancel" (text) and "Save" (primary pill button)
208	- Form validation: Period date required, must be before today
209	
210	**Data Operations:**
211	- On save: `CycleEntryProvider.addEntry(startDate, endDate?, length, notes, isIrregular)`
212	
